column5: We just had a little squal go through London but its over now
Drove through that crap this morning on the 401, it was actually snowing downtown To at Union Station.
whens it gunna be over!!!!!!!!!!!	i want summer now

Was out back with the dog when I heard the wind pick up like a tornado was coming and then it started to "SNOW" and I mean "SNOW"...didn't last long but it was coming down like it had a purpose...  Glad I decided not to try for crappies yesterday and today...would have froze my off!!!
